		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Oops, I forgot the link.  All the stuff is here, source is in 2a03-src.zip.
<br /><a href="http://membler-industries.com/SNES/" class="postlink">http://membler-industries.com/SNES/</a>
<br />
<br />main.asm is kind of a mess, but I guess most of the stuff in there you won't need at all.  The SPC stuff is in spc.asm.  I don't know how much SPC memory got used, but I doubt it's much so there should be plenty of room for more samples.  Let me know if you have any questions about WTF is going on in the source there.

		

