	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It uses 4 channels, DPCM isn't supported.  The BRR compression really aliases the sharpness of the pulse waveforms, though.  I used very tiny samples, so I'm thinking longer samples with the freqs scaled up might help it, I don't know by how much though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
